msgstr "/उस्र/बिन/क्रेनाम"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: konfigurator.docbook:1469
#, no-c-format
msgid "/usr/bin/krusader"
msgstr "/उस्र/बिन/क्रूसेडर"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: konfigurator.docbook:1483
#, no-c-format
msgid "/usr/bin/locate"
msgstr "/usr/bin/स्थान"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: konfigurator.docbook:1497
#, no-c-format
msgid "/bin/mount"
msgstr "/बिन/माउंट"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: konfigurator.docbook:1511
#, no-c-format
msgid "/bin/umount"
msgstr "/बिन/अमाउंट"

#. Tag: replaceable
#: konfigurator.docbook:1525
#, no-c-format
msgid "/usr/bin/updatedb"
msgstr "/usr/bin/updatedb"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default &kompare; is used as external diff utility but you can also use "
"your favorite diff utility &eg; <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/xxdiff/"
"\"><application>xxdiff</application></ulink> or <ulink url=\"https://www.kde."
"org/applications/development/kdiff3/\"><application>KDiff3</application></"
"ulink>, just fill in the full path and enjoy."
msgstr ""
"पूर्वनिर्धारितरूपेण &kompare; बाह्य diff उपयोगितायाः रूपेण उपयुज्यते परन्तु भवान् स्वस्य "
"प्रियं diff उपयोगिता अपि उपयोक्तुं शक्नोति &eg; <ulink url=\"http://furius.ca/"
"xxdiff/\"><अनुप्रयोग>xxdiff</application></ulink> अथवा <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.kde.org/applications/development/kdiff3 /\"><application>KDiff3</"
"application></ulink>, केवलं पूर्णमार्गं पूरयित्वा आनन्दं लभत ।"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: konfigurator.docbook:1540
#, no-c-format
msgid "Packers tab"
msgstr "Packers ट्याब्"

#. Tag: para
#: konfigurator.docbook:1542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Packers</guilabel> tab you will see a list of archive "
"formats. Some are filled and some are empty. The ones that are available "
"(filled) are supported by &krusader;. For them, &krusader; will handle the "
"archives transparently and let you open them as folders (provided you have "
"checked the <guilabel>Browse Archives As Folders</guilabel> item in the "
"<link linkend=\"konfig-archives\">Archives</link> section); otherwise, "
"&krusader; will attempt to invoke an application which opens archives of "
"that type. If a certain archive item is empty, it means that &krusader; "
"could not find the appropriate executables in the configured path. The next "
"archives are supported: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, iso, lha, lzma, rar, "
"rpm, tar, xz, zip and 7z."
msgstr ""
"इति<guilabel> पैकर्स</guilabel> tab भवन्तः archive formats इत्यस्य सूचीं पश्यन्ति । "
"केचन पूरिताः केचन शून्याः। ये उपलभ्यन्ते (पूरिताः) ते &amp;krusader;. तेषां कृते &amp;"
"krusader; अभिलेखागारं पारदर्शकरूपेण सम्पादयिष्यति तथा च भवन्तं तान् पुटरूपेण उद्घाटयितुं "
"ददाति (यद्यपि भवान्...<guilabel> संग्रहणानि पुटरूपेण ब्राउज् कुर्वन्तु</guilabel> item in "
"the<link linkend=\"konfig-archives\"> अभिलेखागारः</link> खंड); अन्यथा &amp;"
"krusader; तत्प्रकारस्य अभिलेखान् उद्घाटयति इति अनुप्रयोगं आह्वयितुं प्रयतते । यदि कश्चन "
"संग्रहवस्तु रिक्तः भवति तर्हि &amp;krusader; विन्यस्तमार्गे समुचितानि कार्यान्वयनीयानि न "
"प्राप्नुवन् । अग्रिमाः अभिलेखागाराः समर्थिताः सन्ति: ace, arj, bzip2, deb, gzip, "
"iso, lha, lzma, rar, rpm, tar, xz, zip तथा 7z ।"

